starvationevasion.client.MegaMawile.model

Class GameOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • starvationevasion.client.model.GameOptions

  • public class GameOptions
extends java.lang.Object
    GameOptions stores all of the information we need to find the server we want to connect to, authenticate our login credentials, and pick a region to begin playing.
